cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DC 

The paper focuses on using deep learning for land-use classification in urban areas, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of Autoregressive Integrated Moving Average (ARIMA) model for forecasting also falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with large-scale data processing and management, which falls under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) sub-category.
